# The released re-ranker checkpoints are vendored via git-lfs (see
# .gitattributes); pip installs fetch the same files from the GitHub release
# on first run instead. The big weights (Maia-3 23M) are NOT in git —
# they auto-download from HuggingFace.

# Bulk simulation outputs (100-game runs etc.): analysis data, not source.
# The curated 6-game demo set in demos/games/ stays tracked.
demos/games/*_sims/
